# Supply-chain defence — Urban Root cross-product policy 2026-05-15
# See: Aero-Calc/repo-clone/docs/saas-lemonsqueezy-threat-research-2026-05-15.md
#
# ignore-scripts=true: neuters postinstall/preinstall hooks. Primary defence
# against the Shai-Hulud npm worm family (Sept 2025 / Nov 2025 / May 2026).
# Tradeoff: native-binary postinstalls (esbuild, sharp) fail visibly until
# you run `npm install --ignore-scripts=false` explicitly.
#
# min-release-age=3: 72-hour cooldown before installing newly-published
# versions. Structurally blocks smash-and-grab waves (chalk/debug Sept 2025,
# eslint-prettier July 2025, axios March 2026) whose attack windows were
# 2-24h. Native to pnpm 9+; npm RFC pending — line documents intent.
ignore-scripts=true
min-release-age=3
